doing his best Hall & Oates.

227
00:14:43,216 --> 00:14:44,967
- Not my finest moment.
- Really?

228
00:14:45,051 --> 00:14:47,512
- No, it wasn't.
- Ben.

229
00:14:47,595 --> 00:14:49,931
He was so cute, I just had to save him.

230
00:14:50,014 --> 00:14:52,850
